                            <comment id="17469741" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 6 Jan 2022 07:15:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay so this is because using &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;camel.component.quartz.start-delayed-seconds = 3&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;then due to that delay then any jobs that was supposed to trigger is misfired and so in 3 sec then 1 task must be triggered that is misfired and then fired asap&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17469775" author="davsclaus" created="Thu, 6 Jan 2022 08:47:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Okay removing the startDelayed option as it causes more pain.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
